 and community members.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 02. Jun 2024) 0aPolitical planningzUnited States. 0aPostmodernismxPolitical aspects. 4aPhilosophy : Postmodernism. 7aPOLITICAL SCIENCE / Public Policy / General.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertSUNY Press eBook Package  Backlist 2000-2013z978311148737340uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/9780791488034?locatt=mode:legacy40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780791488034423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9780791488034/original  a978-3-11-148737-3  SUNY Press eBook Package  Backlist 2000-2013c2000d2013  aGBV-deGruyter-alles